    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_73419291-9121-42B1-AFE6-79886AF16E07" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have the Canvas Teacher app on your <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/docs/DOC-9831-18561185379" target="_blank">iOS</a> or <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/docs/DOC-9758-18555199445" target="_blank">Android</a> device, you can log into the app by searching for your institution, with your institution’s URL, or using a QR code.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="step-title" data-step-uuid="60D87544-35B1-40EA-97EB-CBFBED8F7B29">
    <h2 id="step-title" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Find Your School</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/257/280/original/811cbafc-3686-4f16-ac27-893cf760a026.png" srcset="" alt="Find Your School" height="275" width="561">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_E9FFCA83-8903-4CB1-A2C1-CDB1361A63BF" class="text-block-content">
    <p>When you open the Canvas Teacher App, tap the <strong>Find my school</strong> button [1].</p>
<p>Then, enter your institution’s name in the <strong>Find your school or district </strong>field [2].</p>
<p>For additional help, you can tap the <strong>How do I find my school? </strong>link [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="enter-school-s-canvas-url" data-step-uuid="56522ef4-0e84-4be6-9d48-b6b0d2b4808a">
    <h2 id="enter-school-s-canvas-url" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Enter School's Canvas URL</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/257/284/original/609ac23e-139e-4e14-8997-1fa184f802a2.png" srcset="" alt="Find Your School" height="340" width="387">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_23838daa-8f85-4b22-bcf2-67da3854cfaf" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Alternatively, you can enter your institution's Canvas URL found in the desktop address bar [1].</p>
<p>For additional help, you can tap the <strong>Tap here for help </strong>link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="log-in-with-qr-code" data-step-uuid="DDEA00B2-826C-45A7-B4CB-19685ACF21FB">
    <h2 id="log-in-with-qr-code" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Log In with QR Code</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/257/286/original/429e8c0f-a747-4db5-a3c4-22fb8803824d.png" srcset="" alt="Log In with QR Code" height="630" width="387">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_22C58896-E764-4F61-B94D-42ABF3F2D3B2" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can also log into your Canvas account using the <strong>QR Login</strong> option.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="generate-qr-code-in-browser" data-step-uuid="C4AA9EA7-0E95-4CCF-9BB1-D64044B3560A">
    <h3 id="generate-qr-code-in-browser" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Generate QR Code in Browser</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/257/290/original/9fbe1ed7-49ac-4b55-9408-36c9b055a873.png" srcset="" alt="Genereate QR Code in Browser" height="479" width="456">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_9514653A-4FB6-4694-A488-F43C49FBB913" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In your Canvas browser tab, in Global Navigation, click the <strong>Account</strong> link [1]. Then click the <strong>QR for Mobile Login</strong> link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="scan-qr-code" data-step-uuid="26979122-453F-4DD4-8E04-407445F6C4AC">
    <h3 id="scan-qr-code" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Scan QR Code</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/257/292/original/d0f33d01-9152-4204-9c7c-599957846ff3.png" srcset="" alt="Scan QR Code" height="326" width="808">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_7BDE9F8A-D2DF-41C0-B205-3918E6E1C0D5" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Canvas Teacher app login page, tap the <strong>QR Login</strong> link [1]. </p>
<p>Click the <strong>Next</strong> link [2], then scan the Canvas browser QR code with your device camera [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>
					
				
			
			
			
				
			
			
			
			
			
			
